TITLE:  Direct  Replication  of  a  research  claim  from  Sandra  &  Otto,  2018  in  Cognition  
 
 
 
______  
 
 
 
2.
Authors  (required)  
 
 
 
AUTHORS:   
  
 
 
Daniel  C.  Molden 1  
 
 
 
1  Northwestern  University  
 
 
 
 
 
 

3.
Description  (optional)  
 
3.1.
Please  give  a  brief  description  of  your  study,  including  some  background,  the   
